        <title>Gold Investments</title>
        <subtitle>Prevision for 2016</subtitle>
        <chapter>
          <paragraph>The gold investments in 2016 seem crackling. According to a survey,
            nearly one-fifth of investors expect the price of gold at the end of 2016 to rise by 10%,
            while a fifth thinks that this increase may even reach 20%. Only a minority has a bearish view for the gold price.</paragraph>
